OL,3,CResidents finally given accommodation
OL,4,Cweek on from flood evacuation
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney has been hearing from the
OL,8,Fresidents of Meadow Mill one week on
OL,9,Fsince their apartment building was
OL,10,Fflooded.
OL,12,FResidents left in "complete crisis"
OL,13,Fafter being evacuated from their homes
OL,14,Ffollowing the New Year's Day flooding
OL,15,Fare finally being put into
OL,16,Faccommodation after they were left
OL,17,Fhomeless with no timeframe to return.
