OL,3,CResidents finally given accommodation
OL,4,Cweek on from flood evacuation
OL,6,FThose living in Meadow Mill in
OL,7,FStockport, Greater Manchester, remain
OL,8,Fwithout electricity, heating, and
OL,9,Fwater, more than a week after they
OL,10,Fwere asked to leave the building.
OL,12,FMany have had to pay out of pocket for
OL,13,Faccommodation to ensure a roof over
OL,14,Ftheir heads.
