OL,3,CResidents finally given accommodation
OL,4,Cweek on from flood evacuation
OL,6,FCriticising the "unacceptable" lack of
OL,7,Fresponse from those who own and manage
OL,8,Fthe building, Stockport Council wrote
OL,9,Fto the "organisations we believe are
OL,10,Fresponsible" to "act swiftly to
OL,11,Fprovide the support and information
OL,12,Fresidents need".
OL,14,FIt now says following a meeting with
OL,15,Finsurer AXA, the company has agreed to
OL,16,Fprovide suitable accommodation for the
OL,17,Fresidents for the next seven days.
