OL,3,CResidents finally given accommodation
OL,4,Cweek on from flood evacuation
OL,6,FResponding to the AXA meeting, Cllr
OL,7,FMark Hunter said: "I'm pleased that
OL,8,FAXA has finally stepped up and done
OL,9,Fthe right thing for residents.
OL,11,F"This has been an incredibly difficult
OL,12,Ftime for those affected and ensuring
OL,13,Fthey have somewhere safe and warm to
OL,14,Fstay is welcome news ahead of
OL,15,Fresidents returning to their homes
OL,16,Fsafely as soon as possible."
