OL,3,CResidents finally given accommodation
OL,4,Cweek on from flood evacuation
OL,6,FA CERT spokesperson said they have
OL,7,Fbeen communicating with flat owners
OL,8,Fand landlords "daily" since New Year's
OL,9,FDay and they aim to "have the power
OL,10,Fback on in communal landlord areas" by
OL,11,FMonday, 13 January.
OL,13,FIn a statement, CERT said: "We
OL,14,Funderstand that the uncertainty around
OL,15,Fwhen residents can return to their
OL,16,Fhomes, and whether they will be
OL,17,Freimbursed for their personal costs
OL,18,Fsince the event is very difficult and
OL,19,Fconfusing, and we are sympathetic to
OL,20,Ftheir position.
